## Diffie-Hellman Starter 2
### Solution
You brute-force to get the answer.

### Code
```python
def order(g, p):
	for i in range(2, p):
		if pow(g, i, p) == g:
			return i
		return p
		
p = 28151
for g in range(2,p):
	o = order(g, p) 
	if o == p: 
		print(g) 
		break
```
